11 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
12 OF THE 1ST SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
13 THAT the Oklahoma House of Representatives declares May 4, 2025,
